     <div class="bookname"> 
      <h1>第344章 大开杀戒（第二更）</h1> 
      <div class="bottem1"> 
       <a href="/68_68477/3764873.html">上一章</a> ← 
       <a href="/68_68477/">章节列表</a> → 
       <a href="/68_68477/3766480.html">下一章</a> 
       <a rel="nofollow" href="javascript:;" onclick="addBookMark(3765009,68477);">加入书签</a> 
      </div> 
      <div class="lm">
       推荐阅读：
       <a href="/68_68478/">重生之官途</a>
       <a href="/68_68479/">天影</a>
       <a href="/68_68480/">元气少年</a>
       <a href="/68_68481/">纵横仙荒</a>
       <a href="/68_68482/">超品小神医</a>
       <a href="/68_68476/">拳坛巨星</a>
       <a href="/68_68475/">护花小邪龙</a>
       <a href="/68_68474/">太古帝皇</a>
       <a href="/68_68473/">附身吕布</a>
       <a href="/68_68472/">都市之国术无双</a>
      </div> 
